  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Scheduled abdominal surgery

          -  ASA I-II

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of eye deformity, invasive ophthalmologic surgery, impaired pupil reflex in
             advance

          -  Kown cranial nerve(s) deficit

          -  Infection of the eye

          -  Predicted difficult airway management (DAF Guidelines)

          -  Chronic opioid use (&gt;3 months)

          -  Ongoing treatment with beta-blockers, dopamine antagonists, topical atropine
      </textblock>
